ic optimization model, an statistical robust approach is used\nto generate scenarios for reflecting the temporal inter-dependence of the LMP\nforecast uncertainties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Apr 2023 19:28:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-11"}
