-dependent probability of existence\ncombined with a stochastic spatially correlated Rayleigh NLoS fading component.\nThe developed simulations and analyses rely on this suitable channel model\nunder realistic assumptions of pilot contamination and correlated channels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 8 Apr 2023 00:08:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-11"}
